Michael CUMMINGS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D15-4225 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. September 24, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Pursuant to this court's orders of July 18, 2018, and August 30, 2018, this case is dismissed due to Appellant's failure to file a brief directed to the merits of his appeal.

KELLY, VILLANTI, and BLACK, JJ., Concur.
